About Me

After working in the field of Geomatics in various research and analysis postions (both in the public and private sector) I realized that I wanted to take my career in a different direction. I quit my job, moved to a pal's farm and started learning how to code. Fast forward to now, after graduating from Le Wagon coding bootcamp I am now very excited to say I am a Full Stack Web Developer!
